Class ContainerBuildRule<T>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HasBuildTarget, BuildRule, java.lang.Comparable<HasBuildTarget>

    public class ContainerBuildRule<T>
extends NoopBuildRule
    A dummy BuildRule that stores items in the action graph. This is mainly useful as a "summary" of several build rules, which are generated together, and allows checking if they have all been created via a single build rule lookup in the action graph. This is useful for how the C/C++ support lazily generates actions for the build rule.
